{
  "stem": "11067.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I must tell you, that cabin reeked from 4711 cologne.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But nothing helped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I went-- I wanted to go and find these girls with the medication.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And my timing was bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "A steward was making the rounds of the boat and tried to tell me to go back to sleep and get into my cabin.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I didn't understand him and he didn't understand me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I had a little bit of English.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I had tagged along with my sister to learn English, but it wasn't anything to understand.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Finally, the only way that he could make himself understood was grab my arm, shove me back into the cabin, and close the door.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "All right, my mother said everything was going to be fine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Nothing had been fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "My mother was left on the platform, and I suddenly am on the train with people I don't know, and all these wonderful things are happening.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I finally snuck out and I found the girls.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And they took us into their cabin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They took the other little girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "We got medicine into her and finally got her to sleep.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And in the morning we docked at Harwich.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And we were fed an English breakfast, white toast and tea.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Tea is fine, except that I'd never seen white bread before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And adding up all the things that had happened-- because the steward really giving me a shove into the cabin I thought, you know, maybe this is not friendly.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And so I said to the kids around me when I saw this breakfast, that maybe we shouldn't eat this, because I think they're trying to poison us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "So, of course, a lot of the kids were even younger than me and looked at me like I was crazy.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
